93
00:08:43,790 --> 00:08:45,840
Huang Weijie, don't, Huang Weijie.

94
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:50,280
You fool, why didn't you listen to me?

95
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:58,280
I've gotten smarter.

96
00:09:02,110 --> 00:09:03,200
Huang Weijie,

97
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:08,760
