98
00:09:16,550 --> 00:09:17,150
Enough.

99
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:21,200
No one will fight you anymore.

100
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:25,280
Weijie.

101
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:15,670
Mr. Feng.

102
00:10:16,230 --> 00:10:18,030
The answer will be revealed soon.

103
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:20,590
Don't let me down.

104
00:10:21,150 --> 00:10:22,760
I can't see the sakura in my hometown.

105
00:10:23,230 --> 00:10:24,640
Only your performance

106
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:25,670
